    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>叛逃 AI Skullbot Prime（斯库尔波特·至尊）及其创造者 Dr. Nefarious（尼法瑞厄斯博士）已经接管了银河系中的每一家分拣公司。他们强迫工人们沦为奴隶，以此为博士的生命力提供燃料。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前仅存的一家公司是 <strong>Sorted Inc.（索特有限公司）</strong>。生存意味着必须赢得一份 <strong>Indestructible Contract（不灭合约）</strong>——这份文件将使公司永远无法被收购。为了证明自己有资格获得它，玩家必须征服横跨三个敌对区域的 <strong>24 个关卡</strong>。每过 8 关都会迎来一场** Boss 战**，工人们将把分拣的物品化作武器，在这款支持 1 到 4 人的在线合作游戏中，反击他们的企业统治者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/a922712a0f25331fd4d2685dfef70f2c.poster.avif?t=1771019374\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/a922712a0f25331fd4d2685dfef70f2c.webm?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/a922712a0f25331fd4d2685dfef70f2c.mp4?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>工作器具 (TOOLS OF THE JOB)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sorted Inc.</strong> 正在追寻终极法律护盾：<strong>Indestructible Contract（不灭合约）</strong>。这是一份能让公司永久免于被收购的文件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了赢得这份合约，团队必须证明自己能利用一系列工业机械在混乱中完成分拣。操作 <strong>Stampers（盖章机）</strong>、<strong>Combination units（组合单元）</strong> 以及 <strong>Sorting systems（分拣系统）</strong>，高效处理产品并将其运离空间站，交到等待的客户手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/94c87b85c84dbe7891d8ebd48519d8f6.poster.avif?t=1771019374\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/94c87b85c84dbe7891d8ebd48519d8f6.webm?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/94c87b85c84dbe7891d8ebd48519d8f6.mp4?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>个性装饰 (ACCESSORIZE)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>定制你的工人，穿出风格，分拣出彩。更换头部、戴上帽子、换上酷炫眼部装备并背上背包——毕竟，拯救公司的过程也得赏心悦目。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/9b1040943ca7ce4b5b79c78c0ff14511.poster.avif?t=1771019374\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/9b1040943ca7ce4b5b79c78c0ff14511.webm?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/9b1040943ca7ce4b5b79c78c0ff14511.mp4?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>作战计划 (GAMEPLAN)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在应对每个站台独特的布局和疯狂的险境时，磨炼并精通你的玩法风格。你的机器人是会迎接挑战、脱颖而出，还是会被竞争对手分拣公司彻底击溃？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/6a922e65837b62c851bdec0449b7c486.poster.avif?t=1771019374\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/6a922e65837b62c851bdec0449b7c486.webm?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315490/extras/6a922e65837b62c851bdec0449b7c486.mp4?t=1771019374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
